River Plate won the championship in this round with the following line-ups:

River Plate: Fillol; 
             Saporiti, Pavoni, Passarella, Tarantini; 
             López, Merlo, Alonso;
             González, Luque, Commisso.
             Coach: Labruna.
Tigre:       García;
             Ros, Maiola, Sanz, Márquez;
             Krecevich (83' Pannunzio), Lemme, Fiori (70' Giacopuzzi);
             Montes, Paruzzo, Carrizo.
Referee:     Del Bello.
Field:       Monumental Antonio Vespucio Liberti (River Plate).
Att.:        8.000 tickets.

11' 1-0 Ros (o.g.).
